OL,3,CWoman diagnosed with rare condition
OL,4,Cafter doctors said she was just drunk
OL,6,FA woman discharged from hospital seven
OL,7,Ftimes for being drunk actually had a
OL,8,Frare condition that gave the
OL,9,Fappearance that she was intoxicated.
OL,11,FDespite telling doctors she hadn't
OL,12,Fbeen drinking, medical professionals
OL,13,Ffound elevated levels of alcohol in
OL,14,Fher blood and on her breath.
OL,16,FShe was eventually diagnosed with auto-
OL,17,Fbrewery syndrome (ABS), a condition
OL,18,Fwhich sees fungi in the gut create
OL,19,Falcohol through fermentation.
