OL,3,CWoman diagnosed with rare condition
OL,4,Cafter doctors said she was just drunk
OL,6,FResearchers say awareness of this
OL,7,Fsyndrome, which can have serious
OL,8,Fconsequences for sufferers, is
OL,9,Fessential for proper diagnosis and
OL,10,Fmanagement.
OL,12,FOver two years the woman visited the
OL,13,Femergency department complaining of
OL,14,Fextreme daytime sleepiness and slurred
OL,15,Fspeech.
OL,17,FShe had been on several antibiotic
OL,18,Fcourses for recurrent urinary tract
OL,19,Finfections alongside a proton pump
OL,20,Finhibitor to reduce the amount of acid
OL,21,Fin her stomach.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/7
