OL,3,CWoman diagnosed with rare condition
OL,4,Cafter doctors said she was just drunk
OL,6,FAfter each hospital visit the woman
OL,7,Fwas discharged with the diagnosis of
OL,8,Falcohol intoxication, despite her
OL,9,Freports of no alcohol intake, which
OL,10,Fher family confirmed.
OL,12,FThe patient, who is a mother, needed
OL,13,Fup to two weeks off work after each
OL,14,Fepisode, during which she ate very
OL,15,Flittle.
OL,17,FHer symptoms would get better after
OL,18,Fone to two weeks, but would return
OL,19,Fevery couple of months.
