OL,3,CWoman diagnosed with rare condition
OL,4,Cafter doctors said she was just drunk
OL,6,FOn the third visit, she was even
OL,7,Fcertificated under the Mental Health
OL,8,FAct, as the doctor had concerns for
OL,9,Fself-neglect when she discharged
OL,10,Fherself before psychiatric assessment.
OL,12,FHowever, at her seventh visit the
OL,13,Femergency doctor considered a
OL,14,Fdiagnosis of auto-brewery syndrome,
OL,15,Fand after being prescribed medication,
OL,16,Fshe was referred to a specialist.
